Resource Profile: CH Audit Event with a Basic Auth Token

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epr-fhir/StructureDefinition/ChAuditEventBasicToken Version: 5.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2025-05-22 Computable Name: ChAuditEventBasicToken

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This is the profile for Swiss Audit Events when a transaction is secured with a Basic Authorization Token.

Usage:

  • Derived from this Resource Profile: CH Audit Event with an Extended Auth Token
